@startuml
actor App 
box "Runtime"
participant Orchestrator
database GlobalNode
database LocalNodes
end box


App -[#green]> Orchestrator: Request:\nAlgorithm, data, filters, ...

Orchestrator -[#blue]-> LocalNodes: Control:\nSplit data into k batches
loop over batches
    ref over Orchestrator, LocalNodes, GlobalNode :Training phase using remaining k-1 batches
    ref over Orchestrator, LocalNodes, GlobalNode :Testing phase using current batch
end
Orchestrator -[#blue]-> GlobalNode: Control:\nGlobal UDF for computing CV metrics
GlobalNode -[#red]> Orchestrator: Transfer:\nFinal result

Orchestrator -[#green]> App: Response:\nFinal result
@enduml

